The /public directory contains default web-pages.

   -> 404.html, 422.html, 500.html
     These pages are shown to the user when any one of the HTTP status codes
     are returned. For example, if a page is not found you will see the
     404.html page is displayed.

       List of HTML Status Codes:
         - http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_HTTP_status_codes

   -> robots.txt
     The robots.txt file is for web-crawlers (most notably search engines).
         - http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robots.txt

